            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_150gc' title='Col. 150GC &mdash; HL Deb 28 January 2004 vol 656 c150GC' name='column_150gc' href='#column_150gc' rel='bookmark'>150GC</a>
            than that of murder and manslaughter. We are told that the maximum term of imprisonment is 10 years. Therefore it is in itself a serious offence.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0656P0-01881'>
        <a name='S5LV0656P0_20040128_GCR_56'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-alan-campbell-1' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040128_GCR_56' title='Link to this speech by Mr Alan Campbell' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
